{"tid":418480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Elon Musk 進一步講佢嘅火星殖民計劃，仲有......","createTime":"2017-09-29T15:02:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T06:58:11.000Z","uid":31098,"like":32,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"cf1d8df198db2422ef580c05942c18f405a633ff","tid":418480,"uid":31098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:02:58.000Z","msg":"Elon Musk 喺十個鐘前進一步講解佢嘅火星登陸加殖民計劃：<br />\n<br />\n全片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/S5V7R_se1Xc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FS5V7R_se1Xc&d=8Voj8Bet9WEfHL0REuDRfttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=c310645a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/S5V7R_se1Xc</a><br />\n<br />\n2022 年（5年後！）先射兩支大型貨運火箭去火星，為起基地做準備<br />\n2024 年射多兩支貨運火箭，再加兩支載火箭，登陸火星，起基地<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/225704_577cd74202f28197108adb711b8c02ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F225704_577cd74202f28197108adb711b8c02ea.jpg&h=620e842f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最終希望可以喺火星殖民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/225908_6a51ca3e6bdf7ec7bfd276da77fcab65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F225908_6a51ca3e6bdf7ec7bfd276da77fcab65.jpg&h=f8750336&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/225908_60515619f1b9cb2e4d07fc7d1e9c5d72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F225908_60515619f1b9cb2e4d07fc7d1e9c5d72.jpg&h=ae3fb611&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住佢仲話，既然整到去火星嘅火箭，不如用佢取代飛機做國際交通工具啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/S5V7R_se1Xc?t=41m\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FS5V7R_se1Xc%3Ft%3D41m&d=8Voj8Bet9WEfHL0REuDRfttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=9da0ca98\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/S5V7R_se1Xc?t=41m</a><br />\n<br />\n真係咁做嘅話，去世界各地一個鐘唔使 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1998192a48a659c60448438d7b67088938feb2d","tid":418480,"uid":31098,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:08:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/230847_5b81730a3486116d5e82d7e50d45a4c7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F230847_5b81730a3486116d5e82d7e50d45a4c7.jpg&h=e1033314&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53ec2fa85b11e134e73bfe51bcc800a2db095b67","tid":418480,"uid":26506,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:10:46.000Z","msg":"Suborbital intraplanetary rocket flight 俾人笑到上天 <br />\n老老實實真係可笑嘅 PR gimmick"},{"pid":"7abc924a0b94584a653771851edc84a6fa33cdcc","tid":418480,"uid":629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:10:49.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"865fec7c5269a5ffff8b4fba06ebab11e9844bf1","tid":418480,"uid":31098,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:15:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Suborbital intraplanetary rocket flight 俾人笑到上天 <br />\n老老實實真係可笑嘅 PR gimmick</blockquote><br />\n我其實都覺得大材小用多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211e503bfb11f280c5ce6555af8cd6ea4763a1a3","tid":418480,"uid":17008,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:17:18.000Z","msg":"長距可以<br />\n短距都係hyperloop啦"},{"pid":"2c7ff95f6911af9e37d9ba0e066a4c2a66c0e201","tid":418480,"uid":82641,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:17:54.000Z","msg":"過多幾年 tesla 都唔知破產未啦<br />\n到而家都仲未賺錢"},{"pid":"12d53daf4bf38fe9e32be9bf342510a4b9f9858e","tid":418480,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:18:33.000Z","msg":"都係gimmick<br />\n搵唔到錢搵鬼做<br />\n不過佢想歷史書留名另計"},{"pid":"6eb06b9c0f149ba4dc8a42ef4b5183c05b10845a","tid":418480,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:18:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>長距可以<br />\n短距都係hyperloop啦</blockquote><br />\n唔係距離囉..."},{"pid":"8092d7a1994970ee54f1330233b99ba63921622a","tid":418480,"uid":59886,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:18:47.000Z","msg":"Elon Musk is just an alien tryna go hone"},{"pid":"431b8f1cdad902a6f0b8f59f7d574362a27daeeb","tid":418480,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:18:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>長距可以<br />\n短距都係hyperloop啦</blockquote><br />\n唔係距離問題囉...</blockquote><br />\n[edit]"},{"pid":"7619293dcd5a860bb1fc59f2186674c8d0ccbfab","tid":418480,"uid":10788,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:21:57.000Z","msg":"他接連投入1億美元於建造火箭的SpaceX、7,000萬美元於Tesla電動車、3,000萬美元於太陽能服務SolarCity。<br />\n<br />\n三項經營至今的全新業務，看似不同，但其實都是Musk為實現移民火星不可或缺的技術工具。沒錯，移民火星聽起來是很瘋狂的計劃，可是Musk是很認真在做的<br />\n<br />\n三項野全部係為左移民火星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勁"},{"pid":"283a4c67e0900e92e6d1f19a81ecb84f91c68e56","tid":418480,"uid":26506,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:26:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>他接連投入1億美元於建造火箭的SpaceX、7,000萬美元於Tesla電動車、3,000萬美元於太陽能服務SolarCity。<br />\n<br />\n三項經營至今的全新業務，看似不同，但其實都是Musk為實現移民火星不可或缺的技術工具。沒錯，移民火星聽起來是很瘋狂的計劃，可是Musk是很認真在做的<br />\n<br />\n三項野全部係為左移民火星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勁</blockquote><br />\n創新嘅bottom-up approach啫 <br />\nDARPA, NASA 堆軍事,航太嘢你咪嘆緊"},{"pid":"15227ecb599359e3306dccc43b9afc4ed1464245","tid":418480,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:27:06.000Z","msg":"賣夢想"},{"pid":"8f3554769a4602a9a9aa8a410d376c4223c97567","tid":418480,"uid":19072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:28:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1b23719af3a902b94ced674c60518e1266fa387","tid":418480,"uid":10757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:31:37.000Z","msg":"屌佢 外星人黎架 痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42f0400f93cc6dbabd3b21d43b302dfbe7678ae6","tid":418480,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:39:51.000Z","msg":"去到又點<br />\n冇利潤的話咪又同apollo一樣run唔到落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94744152819029b132216568de27533ff27a7fda","tid":418480,"uid":79563,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:43:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去到又點<br />\n冇利潤的話咪又同apollo一樣run唔到落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n土地就係錢啦<br />\n<br />\n你想像下係1842年買左中環1平方公里地, 持有至2017年今日?<br />\n<br />\n然後諗下2030年係火星搶左20000平方公里地?<br />\n<br />\n你係唔係香港住架？"},{"pid":"6557d7dff9bb393f08a7ca4d7caeac06322b9922","tid":418480,"uid":35870,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:47:07.000Z","msg":"其實上火星係可見嘅將來，講緊一百年來有無咩實際<br />\n作用呢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4e2d8f375873b2a6032e88c3334d2858dacd272","tid":418480,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:47:55.000Z","msg":"其實上火星係可見嘅將來，講緊未來一百年有無咩實際作用呢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌打錯晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3ac175ede2a5e14f9a69dc8f1ba701e10615bc","tid":418480,"uid":73054,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:50:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實上火星係可見嘅將來，講緊未來一百年有無咩實際作用呢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌打錯晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n火星應該唔洗點做環境保護<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c9b2b5eac2566ee3bfbdadaa99fd092916d25e","tid":418480,"uid":124899,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:50:41.000Z","msg":"人類留黎托，咁既精神文化程度，絕種算把喇"},{"pid":"4497cdd2528a62e6abf558af4fe8f2df90e15017","tid":418480,"uid":35870,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:51:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去到又點<br />\n冇利潤的話咪又同apollo一樣run唔到落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n土地就係錢啦<br />\n<br />\n你想像下係1842年買左中環1平方公里地, 持有至2017年今日?<br />\n<br />\n然後諗下2030年係火星搶左20000平方公里地?<br />\n<br />\n你係唔係香港住架？</blockquote><br />\n又唔可以咁講喎<br />\n你係撒哈拉沙漠持有1平方公里地，10年後塊地都係垃圾<br />\n<br />\n正如梅窩d樓咁平，都係咁解"},{"pid":"bbd8b298b010c4f9c376ce7550b60c1d380f83c1","tid":418480,"uid":7764,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:56:27.000Z","msg":"唔好講炒樓，先講生存"},{"pid":"7e1dba9494bd4e44ef710e8c656e03d14feadd12","tid":418480,"uid":35870,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:58:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過多幾年 tesla 都唔知破產未啦<br />\n到而家都仲未賺錢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />true<br />\n我開始覺得佢係賣夢想<br />\n不過世界一定要有呢d咁有冒險精神嘅人<br />\n但冒險唔一定代表會成功，更多時係失敗"},{"pid":"bb3b3f94e8d53e9ddc96ac2bef734688ccc12350","tid":418480,"uid":119480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T15:58:40.000Z","msg":"張火星植民假想圖勁似電路版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e4990d2ceb5a47b390982fa514fb6ad1a49e5ea","tid":418480,"uid":99302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:00:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過多幾年 tesla 都唔知破產未啦<br />\n到而家都仲未賺錢</blockquote><br />\n有股民撐住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12404b9d5ce989eae302adc021ca00517bf2f348","tid":418480,"uid":69120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"