" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n世上最壞既人都係受過高等教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"867da950e5b94af577604fdcf51d41a1bb655fe4","tid":418480,"uid":144406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:18:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>人類留黎托，咁既精神文化程度，絕種算把喇</blockquote><br />\n不過最少上得去嘅都有受過教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n世上最壞既人都係受過高等教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好啦 我錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4cee6f4543d0fcae2b6cf4c46bc5302ab92edba","tid":418480,"uid":39846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:18:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>普通人點承受咁既速度啊？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n暫時仲係gimmick 黎。<br />\n天氣，航道等最複習嘅問題佢都冇提過。我諗要頂級a/i 先run 得到。所以聽住先囉。"},{"pid":"650e217fb00fce0007e75528c4d0d6a430af7636","tid":418480,"uid":144406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:19:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一係就改變人類唔使呼吸氧氣，食嘢就光合作用，<br />\n<br />\n一係就改變火星地表適合人類居住啊，如果唔係喺長居太空艙生不如死</blockquote><br />\n掘地下基地會唔會睇落好少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b12d1ec57d942069574e1e991217bef3149835f","tid":418480,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:19:24.000Z","msg":"其實而家科技仲未可以用少能源運大量物資離開地球<br />\n<br />\n射支火箭都要計住計住個負重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fffa78bc933bd60371ca4ba283fd4872a57e397f","tid":418480,"uid":39846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:20:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>越黎越覺得原本人類係住火星<br />\n<br />\n玩爛左就搬左過地球<br />\n<br />\n而家又搬番去火星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n金星似啲。火星理論上係我哋太陽系內少數人類仲有機會生存到嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19bba64483a926537d98a476aa4298e9ecdc2091","tid":418480,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:21:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>普通人點承受咁既速度啊？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n暫時仲係gimmick 黎。<br />\n天氣，航道等最複習嘅問題佢都冇提過。我諗要頂級a/i 先run 得到。所以聽住先囉。</blockquote><br />\n唔關事, 係closed-cycle火箭本身問題"},{"pid":"b419efda6ad222f9adfe5c92d12a69f4997d84e8","tid":418480,"uid":7764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:21:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一係就改變人類唔使呼吸氧氣，食嘢就光合作用，<br />\n<br />\n一係就改變火星地表適合人類居住啊，如果唔係喺長居太空艙生不如死</blockquote><br />\n掘地下基地會唔會睇落好少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n地下基地而家咪有囉，每日進進出出地鐵站，成個香港咁大嘅地下基地，但如果唔俾你出街，長居地鐵站你會點"},{"pid":"0b818ce6b5b66c8f2e3f3b94f239523fa7808538","tid":418480,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:30:59.000Z","msg":"幾時先可以做到龍珠世界咁<br />\n想去其他星球飛過去就得輕輕鬆鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0d4f768c99d1dea12a1d9353388941e79df28d0","tid":418480,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:33:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84423f505d4361059a10576218383c363f04fa8f","tid":418480,"uid":31098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:52:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁做犯唔犯法？</blockquote><br />\n喺香港，佢會被指「影響既得利益者利益」，跟手被犯法"},{"pid":"2ab614a41a8522acd19d6dd5d2da7464f53ce9fe","tid":418480,"uid":71133,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:52:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一係就改變人類唔使呼吸氧氣，食嘢就光合作用，<br />\n<br />\n一係就改變火星地表適合人類居住啊，如果唔係喺長居太空艙生不如死</blockquote><br />\n香港人住埋d狗竇都未死你擔心太空人?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"644ba9dd7bde8980c3ab323066ff6f04c94ca181","tid":418480,"uid":55511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T17:01:57.000Z","msg":"香港政府果千幾億擺係佢度都好過用黎起高鐘啦"},{"pid":"ed4bebf1ae83c74fbc8c8185bbace1971c372212","tid":418480,"uid":28549,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T17:08:13.000Z","msg":"老老竇竇<br />\n當初哥倫布發現左新大陸就話有大量資源同奴隸, 皇帝先比咁多錢搞姐<br />\n火星有咩資源值得搞, 甚至乎要人類移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8abf75c020d360070c4651da5f8405753de1ba1a","tid":418480,"uid":144113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T17:23:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>普通人點承受咁既速度啊？</blockquote><br />\nagger...以後搭個飛機(火箭)都要受訓著太空衣既話搵鬼搭"},{"pid":"7b11bf738592a78fd7b1aba6c5339066cc0babfe","tid":418480,"uid":41325,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T17:26:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老老竇竇<br />\n當初哥倫布發現左新大陸就話有大量資源同奴隸, 皇帝先比咁多錢搞姐<br />\n火星有咩資源值得搞, 甚至乎要人類移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得係做試驗 <br />\n喺火星試吓人類可唔可以喺地球以外嘅星球搞殖民<br />\n因為太陽系外一定有其他星球都可以搞殖民<br />\n火星近近地試吓先 如果之後有技術出到太陽系 到時唔會冇經驗"},{"pid":"140e085ca4b53ff0bb3288f267ce9fafa45e714b","tid":418480,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T17:28:40.000Z","msg":"金仔呢鋪有得翻身喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}